<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Success</title>
    <style>
        @import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:100,100italic,200,200italic,300,300italic,regular,italic,500,500italic,600,600italic,700,700italic,800,800italic,900,900italic);
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        }
        body{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            /* background: #161623; */
            /* background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #404141, #ddd, #404141); */
            /* background: linear-gradient(-45deg,#64ab9c,#cca185,#84ca81,#d8c192); */
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #ddd,#ccc,#5ac1ad, #17ad8e);
            /* background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: animate 5s ease infinite; */
        }
        /* @keyframes animate{
            0%{
                background-position: 0 50%;
            }
            50%{
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }
            100%{
                background-position: 0 50%;
            }
        } */
        body::before{
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(#f00,#17ad8e);
            clip-path: circle(15% at 68% 84%);
        }
        body::after{
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(#17ad8e,#137dd3);
            clip-path: circle(20% at 28% 20%);
        }
        .container{
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .container .card{
            position: relative;
            width: 320px;
            height: 400px;
            margin: 30px;
            box-shadow: 20px 20px 50px rgb(0, 0, 0,0.5);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-left: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .container .card .content{
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .container .card .content h2{
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            right: 8px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: rgba(47, 48, 48, 0.32);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .container .card .content h3{
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #333;
            z-index: 1;
            text-shadow: 0 0.5px 2.5px #333;
        }
        .container .card .content p{
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #222;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        h4{
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .container .card .content a{
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            background-size: 260%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #32be8f, #096244,#32be8f);
            color: #fff;
            display: block;
            width: 70%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            transition: 0.4s;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
        }

        /* .container a{
            color: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #fff;
            background-size: 200%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #32be8f, #38d39f, #32be8f);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            width: 70%;
            transition: 0.4s;
        } */
        .container a:hover{
            background-position: right;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>MA Ansari<br>Health Care</h2>
                <h3>Id: <%=id%></h3>
                <p>Your appointment has been succesfully booked. Kindly check your Email and SMS for appointment date and time.</p>
                <h4>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-Thank You</h4><br>
                <a href="/appointment">Book Another</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>